private PivotPointsHighLow _pphl;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;

// In OnData()
if (_pphl.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "pivotpointshighlow", _pphl.Current.Value);
}
